# cocktailfyi — Python Cocktail Library Demo
Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 920
Set Height 620
Set Shell "zsh"
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Padding 20

# Python engine demo
Type "python demo.py"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# API search
Type `curl -s 'https://cocktailfyi.com/api/search/?q=margarita' | jq '.results[:3][] | {name, type}'`
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 2s
